Telemarketing Sales Coordinator
Confidential Company -
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 05:49:06
Ref. JB3045247
Job Description
•	Obtain names and telephone numbers of potential customers from the system in order to contact them.
•	Contact customers by telephone to persuade them purchase extended warranty policies.
•	Explain services and prices, and answer questions from customers.
•	Obtain customers info and enter sales orders into computers.
•	Schedule appointments for sales representatives to visit prospective customers.
•	Record names, addresses, purchases, and reactions of prospects contacted.
•	Report sales and activities to management on daily/weekly basis.
•	Collect customers’ feedback and create ideas to improve sales.
Skills
Speak and understand Arabic well
Good Sales skills
